com.agorapulse.gru

Interface HttpStatusShortcuts

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ResponseDefinitionBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultResponseDefinitionBuilder

    public interface HttpStatusShortcuts
    Provides HTTP statuses' shortcuts for expect block so they can be used without additional imports.
